This is a blogging/social media website created using flask.
to check it out go to blog-usingflask.herokuapp.com

Key features-
1.Users can write posts.
2.Users can follow/unfollow each other.
3.Users can send private messages to each other, like a chat app.
4.Users can have a profile picture either by gravatar or by uploading the picture using edit profile.
5.Live language translation capabilities.
6.Full In-Text search feature.
7.Popups, try to hover your mouse over a post's author.
